import React from "react"; import "../../styles/collective.css" const Booking = () =>(
BOOKINGS AND BUSINESS INQUIRIES
If you want to book a free consultation or have any questions, do not hesitate to reach out. I generally have a waiting list for website builds but if you send me a message I can give you an ETA as to when I'll be available.

You can also message me with any questions related to social media promotions or collaborations. I'm pretty busy at the moment, but I am definitely open to discussing some new branding partnerships.
) export default Booking;
